title: What time is Strictly Come Dancing on tonight?
text:
What time is Strictly Come Dancing on tonight? By WMNdellis | Posted: October 17, 2015 Claudia and Tess What time is Strictly Come Dancing on tonight? X 
Copy link to paste in your message / Comments (0) 
Last week Anthony and Oti were voted off the show and now it's time for the celebs to dance and do battle again. 
Tonight they'll take to the stage again to perform their fancy footwork in front of the judging panel. 
The lowest on the leader board will leave the show tomorrow.Tune in from 6.30pm.
